聆听 BERWYN 毫无歉意的新单曲“I AM BLACK” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-berwyn-new-unapologetic-single-i-am-black-debut-album-3756627?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-berwyn-新无歉意单曲《我是黑人》首张专辑Kyann-Sian WilliamsThu, 16 May 2024 16:12:09 +0000 Music NewsNewsRapSoulUK rap https://www.nme.com/?p=3756627 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伯温。照片来源：TJ Sawyerr" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我真的很想在世界上创造一个机会，让人们可以以积极的方式说出这三个词”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-berwyn-new-unapologetic-single-i-am-black-debut-album-3756627">聆听 BERWYN 毫无歉意的新单曲“I AM BLACK”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伯温。照片来源：TJ Sawyerr" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Berwyn-Neighbours-Press-Shot-Photo-Credit-TJ-Sawyerr-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/berwyn">BERWYN</a>发行了一首强大的新单曲，名为“I AM BLACK”——您可以在下面收听。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/berwyn-romford-interview-tape-2-2972935">BERWYN：罗姆福德失败者的赤裸裸的说唱正在帮助那些有需要的人</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位出生于特立尼达的歌手兼说唱歌手上个月带着胜利的复出歌曲《Neighbours》回归。他发行了这首深情歌曲的两个版本；他首先放弃了一段由钢琴驱动的独奏，然后 DJ 和制作人<a href="/artists/fred-again">Fred 再次</a>重新混音了这首歌。</p><p>本周早些时候（5 月 14 日），BERWYN 发行了《I AM BLACK》——这是一首充满赞歌且大胆的单曲，传达了对黑人真实而诚实的描述。这首歌曲也“以沉重的悲伤为基础”，“揭示了全国及其他地区许多与他处境相同的人的严酷现实”。 </p><p><iframe title="BERWYN - 我是黑人（官方展示）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zv4ySOzp3PM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> BERWYN 谈到写作过程时说道：“我真的很想在世界上创造一个机会，让人们可以以积极的方式说出这三个词。”</p><p> 《I AM BLACK》是 BERWYN 写过的最困难的唱片之一，因为它借鉴了他九岁时离开特立尼达的父亲并搬到伦敦罗姆福德与祖母住在一起的经历。</p><p>在谈到这段经历时，他解释道：“我离开了一个肤色并不那么重要的国家，[所以]从黑人转向罗姆福德——你被迫陷入生存的困境。”</p><p>这位 28 岁的歌手尚未宣布他的第一张录音室专辑的发行日期，但《I AM BLACK》预计也会出现在这张唱片中。根据一份新闻稿，BERWYN 最近的歌曲是他在网上暗示的“传闻中的首张专辑的诱人味道”。</p><p>目前还不清楚他之前的单曲，如<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/berwyn-path-to-satisfaction-single-3337459">雷鬼风格的《Path To Satisfaction》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/berwyn-has-shared-two-new-songs-3450-and-chasing-lights-demo-3366926">阴沉的《3450》和乐观的《Chasing Lights (Demo)》</a>或去年的《Bulletproof》是否会出现在他备受期待的唱片中。 </p><p><iframe title="BERWYN - Bulletproof（官方展示）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/T6aPv6zRwhU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> BERWYN 在发行获得<a href="/tag/mercury-prize">水星奖</a>提名的首张混音带“DEMOTAPE/VEGA”后于 2020 年声名鹊起。他深情的音色为他赢得了无数赞誉，包括在 2022 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/awards">BandLab NME 奖</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/berwyn-wins-best-new-act-from-the-uk-supported-by-music-venue-trust-bandlab-nme-awards-2022-3172460">中获得英国最佳新人奖</a>。他还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pa-salieu-wins-bbc-sound-of-2021-2851106">BBC Sound Of 2021榜单</a>上排名第三。</p><p>最近，BERWYN 和英国说唱明星 Young Teflons 出现在北伦敦说唱明星 Rimzee 的第四张混音带“Feed The Streets”的“杂志”中。去年五月，这位伦敦人还在 Steel Banglez 的《Things Change》中献声。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-berwyn-new-unapologetic-single-i-am-black-debut-album-3756627">聆听 BERWYN 毫无歉意的新单曲“I AM BLACK”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
