q-tip-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/q-tip-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/q-tip-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/q-tip">Q-Tip</a>因其“前瞻性的艺术视野”而获得伯克利音乐学院的荣誉博士学位。</p><p>本月早些时候，说唱传奇人物、爵士乐艺术家莱迪西和波多黎各乐队领军吉尔伯托·圣罗莎都获得了这所著名音乐学院的荣誉。</p><p>上周六（5 月 11 日），这位<a href="/artists/a-tribe-called-quest">“A Tribe Called Quest”</a>成员在 Instagram 上为自己和其他获奖者庆祝，并附上了一张他戴着定制帽子、穿着礼服、围巾上写着“黑人卓越”的照片。</p><p> “再次感谢伯克利的人们所授予的荣誉，”他写道。 “与亲爱的朋友@ledisi 和新朋友@santarosalive 分享美好时光，恭喜 2024 届毕业生！我还在捏[捏表情符号]#berkleecollegeofmusic。”</p><p>查看下面帖子中的屏幕截图。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Q-Tip 获得伯克利音乐学院荣誉博士学位：“仍然捏着[我自己]” <a href="https://t.co/iGBex1BmK7">pic.twitter.com/iGBex1BmK7</a></p><p> — HipHopDX (@HipHopDX) <a href="https://twitter.com/HipHopDX/status/1789671104178720927?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 5 月 12 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> <a href="https://www.berklee.edu/berklee-now/news/berklee-honors-ledisi-q-tip-and-gilberto-santa-rosa-at-commencement" target="_blank" rel="noopener">伯克利学院</a>表示，Q-Tip 因其“前瞻性的艺术视野，将说唱、爵士乐和其他风格与具有社会意识的歌词融为一体，以及他作为制作人、演员、教育家和文化大使的影响力”而获奖。 。</p><p>该学院还分享了这位纽约说唱歌手在毕业班演讲中的一句话：“选择[艺术家]这条道路确实是一个勇敢的选择。你的任务是在个人生活中保持勇敢，在智力和本能之间找到平衡……不要让错误的选择定义你，而是要完善你。”</p><p>除了他的博士学位之外，Q-Tip 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-roll-hall-of-fame-2024-ozzy-osbourne-cher-and-more-to-be-inducted-3749163">A Tribe Called Quest 的其他成员今年也入选了摇滚名人堂</a>。他们与<a href="/artists/kool-and-the-gang">Kool &amp; The Gang</a> 、 <a href="/artists/mary-j-blige">Mary J. Blige</a> 、 <a href="/artists/cher">Cher</a> 、 <a href="/artists/foreigner">Foreigner</a> 、 <a href="/artists/dave-matthews-band">Dave Matthews Band</a> 、 <a href="/artists/peter-frampton">Peter Frampton</a>和<a href="/artists/ozzy-osbourne">Ozzy Osbourne</a>一起被列入表演者类别。</p><p> A Tribe Called Quest 的 Jarobi White 在 Instagram 上写道：“哇！！！ @qtiptheabstract @alishaheed 我们做到了！菲菲，我们让你进入名人堂！希望你在这里。好吧，我知道你在看……操是的！！！哈哈。所有的求索者，我们发自内心的感谢你们！！！！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C6C-YEhr-NK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66